TRANSCENDENT V: SYNAPSE (The Neural Parasite) 

Role: Saboteur / Strategic Hijacker / Resource Vampire Theme: A bio-mechanical entity that thrives on the resources and structural integrity of its host. 

1. INFECTION STAGES (Leveling System) 

Synapse evolves through milestones that break the enemy's logic and physical limits. 

Level: 1 

Stage: Spore 

Unlockable Ability: Neural Tether: Links 2+ enemies. 40% of damage dealt to one is shared across the link. 

Level: 2 

Stage: Distortion 

Unlockable Ability: Visual Interference: Glitches enemy optics. Screens flicker/blur, making it nearly impossible to aim. 

Level: 3 

Stage: Apex 

Unlockable Ability: Structural Decay: Every hit reduces the target's Maximum HP permanently for the match. 

Level: 4 

Stage: Overmind 

Unlockable Ability: Collective Agony: When one linked enemy is stunned or debuffed, all other linked enemies receive the same effect simultaneously. 

2. THE FOUR STRAINS (Combat Logic) 

Strain A: The Wasting (Damage Focus) 

Lvl 1: DoT scales with the target's movement speed. 

Lvl 2: Reduces target healing by 25%. 

Lvl 3: Vulnerability Protocol: Targets take +30% damage from all sources. 

Lvl 4: Organ Failure: Once a target reaches 15% HP, they are instantly executed by a viral burst. 

Strain B: The Paralyzer (Crowd Control) 

Lvl 1: Slows fire rate/movement by 10% per hit. 

Lvl 2: Freezes active ability cooldowns for 4 seconds. 

Lvl 3: Hard Lockdown: Stuns the target for 3 seconds at max stacks. 

Lvl 4: System Purge: When a stun ends, the targetâ€™s all ability cooldowns are reseted. 

Strain C: The Parasite (Leech & Redirection) 

Lvl 1: Pain Mirror: 60% of damage Synapse takes is transferred to linked enemies. Synapse only takes 20% total actual damage. 

Lvl 2: Restores 5% Ultimate charge per second of contact. 

Lvl 3: Cooldown Vampire: Drains a ready enemy ability to reset Synapse's cooldowns. 

Lvl 4: Genome Steal: Synapse permanently copies the highest stat (Speed, Armor, or Attack) of his current host. 

Strain D: The Gravity Well (Positioning & Weight) 

Lvl 1: Heavy Burden: Every hit increases the target's "Weight." Jump height is reduced by 10% per stack. 

Lvl 2: Engine Stall: If an enemy tries to use a dash or flight ability, they are instantly pulled to the ground and take impact damage. 

Lvl 3: Magnetic Vortex: Two enemies infected with Strain D are physically pulled toward each other. If they collide, they are both stunned for 2 seconds. 

Lvl 4: Event Horizon: The infected target becomes a "Singularity," pulling nearby teammates toward them and preventing anyone within 20m from escaping. 

3. ULTIMATE: TOTAL SYSTEM FAILURE (V2) 

Synapse releases a global pulse. Every infected enemy suffers: 

Base: 20% Current Max HP as True Damage. 

The Pandemic Bonus: Deals an extra 5% damage for every other infected enemy within a 50m radius of the target. 

Silence: Disables all abilities for 8 seconds. 

4. PASSIVE: GHOST IN THE MACHINE 

Invisible Threads: Off-radar and no name tag beyond 50m. 

Counter-Hacking: If an enemy tries to debuff Synapse, the effect is reflected back to the sender at 2x potency. 
